sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Cmd as m2e/start_session
    participant Queue as Event queue
    participant FSM as fsm::v2 FSM
    participant Ctx as FsmContext
    participant Bsp as ev_board_support
    participant Iso as ISO15118_ev
    participant E2M as e2m/state

    Cmd->>Queue: StartSession event
    Queue->>FSM: feed(StartSession)
    FSM->>Ctx: enter SlacMatching
    Ctx->>Bsp: slac_trigger_matching()
    Ctx->>E2M: state=SlacMatching

    Bsp-->>Queue: SlacState(MATCHED)
    Queue->>FSM: feed(SlacState)
    FSM->>Ctx: enter V2GNegotiating
    Ctx->>Iso: iso_start_charging(mode,...)
    Ctx->>E2M: state=V2GNegotiating

    Iso-->>Queue: IsoPowerReady
    Queue->>FSM: feed(IsoPowerReady)
    FSM->>Ctx: enter Charging
    Ctx->>Bsp: set_cp(C), allow_power_on(true)
    Ctx->>E2M: state=Charging
